          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The average intensity was 109 particles/spill."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The number of incident ions was recorded by the",
                "secondary-electron monitor SEETRAM placed before the",
                "production target."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE",
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Inverse geometry."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors.  The ions of interest were identified by",
                "combining measurements of their magnetic rigidity,",
                "energy loss, and time of flight.  The plastic",
                "scintillators mounted at the dispersive intermediate",
                "and achromatic focal planes, were used to determine",
                "the horizontal positions of the fragments and their",
                "time of flight.  At the final focal plane two",
                "multiwire chambers provided the position measurement",
                "for the calibrations.  Finally, from the energy loss",
                "measurement in the ionisation chamber the nuclear",
                "charge was obtained, since all the produced fragments",
                "were fully stripped."
              ]
            }
          ],
